/Rect [ 59.9998 166.669 553.331 474.668 ]
/Subtype /Widget
/F 4
/P 478 0 R
/T (item51)
/V (This SAR is being filed regarding suspicious activity involving Acme LLC\054 an import\057export business\054 which was discovered on June 25\054 2024\056 The activity raised suspicion due to unusual cash patterns and multiple day deposits that appeared to be structured to evade reporting requirements\056 Between May 1\054 2024\054 and May 15\054 2024\054 the subject engaged in multiple cash deposits and funds transfers totaling \04419\054500\05650\054 with transactions that included cash deposits shortly after large withdrawals and wire transfers to unrelated third parties without clear business relationships\056 Supporting documentation includes transaction records detailing cash deposits and funds transfers\054 with specific transactions noted\072 a cash deposit of \0444\054500\05650 on May 2\054 2024\054 followed by a funds transfer of \0445\054000\05600 on May 5\054 2024\054 and additional cash withdrawals and transfers on subsequent dates\056 The subject declined to explain the large cash deposits when questioned\056 The suspicious activity is not isolated\054 as it relates to prior SAR filings\054 and there is an adverse media report indicating that the subject is under investigation\056 The financial institution\054 Example Community Bank\054 located in Dallas\054 NY\054 has retained all records related to this SAR for five years\056 Further investigation is recommended to assist law enforcement in understanding the context and purpose of these transactions\056)
/DA (\057HeBo 9 Tf 0 g)
/FT /Tx
/Type /Annot
/Ff 4096
/AP <<
/N 768 0 R
>>
